    <div class="slide">
        <h1>Understanding AI and Data Security Risks</h1>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Data Breaches:</strong> AI systems can be targets for cyberattacks.</li>
            <li><strong>Bias in AI:</strong> AI models trained on biased data can lead to unfair or discriminatory outcomes.</li>
            <li><strong>Accidental Data Exposure:</strong> Improperly configured AI systems can inadvertently expose sensitive data.</li>
            <li><strong>Lack of Transparency:</strong> Understanding how AI makes decisions can be challenging, posing security risks if vulnerabilities are hidden.</li>
        </ul>
